name: Evaldas Kalade
note:
Hi Evaldas! I represent an outstaffing company Remote Helpers. We provide our clients all over the world with remote employees in IT & Marketing services! Might you be interested in hearing more?

Hello Oksana. IT and Marketing could be our future needs. As for now we are looking for more sales. If you could offer any sales helpers in Ukraine or other markets that could be interesting.

Thank you for your reply!
Candidates we offer you to hire can work in the following positions: Lead Generators, Sales specialists, Designers (Interior, Graphic, Illustrators), Video editors, Developers, Recruiters, Project managers, SEO, PPC, Financiers, Personal Assistants etc.
We can set a call to see if we can find a fit for you and of course explain our model if you are interested.

Lead generators or sales specialists could be interesting options to get more information.

Great! I suggest going out for a short call where we can discuss your needs and we can tell you more about the services we provide. When is it the best time for you?

We can organize short video meeting any time. Possibly today 4–5 pm (UTC +3)

Sure, I can suggest tomorrow 1PM, 2PM and 3PM, Lithuanian time. Will that work for you?

If so, please send me your email, I will create a Google meeting.

2 p.m Lithuanian time is ok. Evaldas@kinetus.lt

Thanks! Sent you the link to the meeting to your email. Looking forward to our call.
